sequenceDiagram
    participant R as Registry (ghcr.io/opensource-distroless)
    participant GH as GitHub Action (Base Assembler)
    participant Sec as Security (Cosign/Trivy)
    
    GH->>R: Pull `artifacts-[glibc, openssl, zlib, tzdata]`
    R-->>GH: Download 4 trusted tarballs
    
    GH->>Sec: `cosign verify` 4 intermediate layers
    Sec-->>GH: Pass (Identities Match OIDC)
    
    GH->>GH: Construct `FROM Scratch` Dockerfile 
    GH->>GH: Unpack layers + Build /etc/passwd rootfs
    
    GH->>Sec: Aggregate 4 JSON SBOMs into base-sbom
    
    GH->>R: Push monolithic OS OS (base:latest)
    GH->>Sec: `cosign sign` Final OCI Manifest
